PrecisOrder exempting the LAURENTIAN PILOTAGE AUTHORITY from the requirement to conduct the internal audit referred to in subsection 131(3) of the Financial Administration Act for the next three fiscal years, on the grounds that the benefits to be derived from such audits do not justify their cost.
